  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of vegetable oil in a large wok or frying pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the sliced red chili and cook for 1 minute more.",
    "Add the shrimp and cook until pink and fully cooked, about 2 minutes.",
    "Add the pandan leaves, coconut milk, tamarind paste, soy sauce, sugar, and salt. Stir well to combine.",
    "Add the noodles to the wok or frying pan and stir-fry for 2-3 minutes, or until the noodles are well coated with the sauce.",
    "Transfer the noodles to a serving dish and garnish with chopped scallions and cilantro.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed."
